title: BBC Radio 1 Annie Mac Mash Up 02/10/2009
description:
Friday 2nd October

LIVE FROM NYC


Annie is LIVE from The Big Apple...New York City!!!

The city that never sleeps, the home of disco, the Yankees, yellow cabs and much more...

We are covering every corner of the dancefloor with a NY twist...

PLUS true dance music legend Armand Van Helden is hanging out in the studio, talking about NYC and playing us some of his favourite records...

And we have a mini mix from Sweden's Miike Snow.
